Package bobaTea

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BobaDrink
    created a sub class that overrides the drinkitem super classes methods implementing getcost, overriding the size methods and the tostring
    cashRegister
    a cash register class that will keep track of the grand total and add drinks and desserts to two array lists of drinks and desserts
    CoffeeDrink
    created a sub class called coffee drink that overrides the drinkitem super classes methods implementing abstract getcost, overriding the size methods, sweetness methods, milk methods, and the tostring method
    Cookie
    this is a sub class that extends the dessert item super class
    Coupon
    this class models a coupon object with a given item to which it can be applied and a percentage amount discount
    DessertItem
    created a dessertItem class that will be the super class for all of the dessert items
    DrinkItem
    a drinkitem super class that will hold many of the common factors that will be used in both boba and coffee
    Macaroon
    a macaroon sub class that extends the cookie class
    Pastry
    this is a sub class the overrides some of the dessert item methods
    Receipt
    a receipt class that takes care of holding the drinks and desserts to be displayed in the end as a receipt
    tester
    created a tester class with main that will be implementing all of my other classes into the main boba tea lounge.
